text:
Can #COVID19 be transmitted through mosquito bites? 
 
No - the new coronavirus is a respiratory virus which spreads mainly through droplets when an infected person coughs or sneezes, or through droplets of saliva or discharge from the nose. https://t.co/jjWH2JikVZ
